{"tid":2019629,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"光復中環：侵侵叫停40億聯邦退休金投資中國, 但其他呢？","createTime":"2020-05-16T12:03:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T15:33:22.000Z","uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"acd044845125c002ce608c8d56c12afe92c95293","tid":2019629,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T12:03:49.000Z","msg":"白宮叫停40億美金聯邦退休基金只係冰山一角， 其實美國州份退休基金一早就已經投資左中國人權有問題的公司啦！<br />\n<br />\n白宮傳出消息話要阻止聯邦儲蓄退休基金投資中國股票或公司，主要原因係因為投資喺&quot;MSCI ACWI ex USA IMI&quot; 代表會投資到起損害美國國家安全同違反人道主義的中國公司 。<br />\n<br />\n但係喺退休基金世界內，其實US$4 billion 唔算多。<br />\n<br />\n美國30大嘅州份退休投資基金一共有 US$2,900 billion (2016) asset under management (AUM) 而全球10大私人企業退休基金內有8間 美國私人企業退休基金擁有US$570 billion (2018) AUM。<br />\n<br />\n而美國州份退休基金一早就投資左好多中國人權有問題的公司啦。<br />\n<br />\n上年3月BBC已經有報道話加州同紐約教師退休投資基金各自都有投資於海康威視HIKVISION (002415 (SHE) ) 依間嘢出名提供監控設備包括起新疆集中營內使用。<br />\n<br />\n今年3月，白宮更調查加州教師退休投資基金有冇投資於中國軍工相關嘅公司。<br />\n<br />\n大家諗下下一步應該要點做？<br />\n<br />\n#LiberateCentral<br />\n<br />\n////////////////////////////////////////////////////<br />\nFacebook: Liberate Central 光復中環<br />\nTelegram: <a href=\"http://t.me/HKFinanceFellow\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKFinanceFellow&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BTY9GQwUZQLLS4G4eGYLUm4%3D&h=2a5305dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/HKFinanceFellow</a><br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"http://Twitter.com/HKFinanceFellow\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FTwitter.com%2FHKFinanceFellow&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BTY9GQwUZQLLS4G4eGYLUm4%3D&h=a5192b44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Twitter.com/HKFinanceFellow</a><br />\nTg報料: @HKFinanceFellowBot<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-china-calpers-idUSKBN20Y2GS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-usa-china-calpers-idUSKBN20Y2GS&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BTY9GQwUZQLLS4G4eGYLUm4%3D&h=b6fd95ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?